Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.49,0:21:11.48,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}縱使深陷天大的謊言中
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.48,0:21:15.60,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我也仍想愛下去
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.85,0:21:18.87,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}夜色滿溢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.87,0:21:21.13,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}配合著步伐
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.13,0:21:26.95,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}時鐘停擺 淡淡的詛咒纏繞著我
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.95,0:21:31.46,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}你的反應總是在逃避
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.98,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}如果只是想重來而已
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.98,0:21:40.30,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}那你這樣吊著我又是何必
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.30,0:21:44.84,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我想知道我的心該放在哪裡
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.84,0:21:49.35,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}遲早都會迎來結束
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.35,0:21:52.17,ED-CH,,0,0,50,,{\an9\fad(360,360)\blur3}我早就清清楚楚
